              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                Chapter Two 读书＋上课笔记<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>In the past, the history is all about the heroes, elite. <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Social history - inequalities, suppress, marxists, concerned with class, focus on the poor and the powerless.   etc - using quantitative methods, - nature science, statistics - 1960s <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>In social history, your life depend on your class<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Cultural history - more micro, related to the conduct of people in everyday life - using anthropological methods -1970-80s - more soft<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>In cultural history, your life depend on identity, (gender is a part of the identity). Identity has replaced the class. There won't be a word of class. <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>text: a film, an advertisement is a text <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Different between social and cultural history: <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>focused group: a shift from the poor to the elite/ middle class<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>methods: a shift from natural science, quantitative methods to anthropology. <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>key words: a shift from class to identity <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>Why there's a shirt of historiography? from 1960s to 1980s. <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>01. the decline of the USSR, and the decline of the Marxism. <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>02. the decline/failure of the progressive movement in America, <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>e.g. 1960s theres a civil movement in America <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>e.g. 1968 student movement in France - what did the French communist party do?<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>03. emergency of the post-colonialism? - li wei<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>04. economic change - a shift from Fordism to post-Fordism 福特制<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>因为class之间的关系已经不能解释为什么那些people没有rebel，the failure of the progressive movement ，所以肯定还有另外一个factor在之前起作用，这个factor就是culture -- that's why switch from social to cultural history <div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>
