          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11685235/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/11685235/" class="">第73页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/silenceapostle/" class=" " title="向沉默下拜">向沉默下拜</a>
                (habitually contradictory)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="11685235">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">除了采用上文所说的新定义之外，年鉴学派的历史学家还对微观历史产生了兴趣。用Giovanni Levi的话来说：

...turned away from the &quot;great Marxist or functionalist systems&quot; by reducing the scale of their observation of historical processes so as to &quot;obtain a more realistic description of human behavior.&quot; They saw social action as &quot;the result of an individual's constant negotiatio...</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-03-05 11:08</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                除了采用上文所说的新定义之外，年鉴学派的历史学家还对微观历史产生了兴趣。用Giovanni Levi的话来说：<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div><blockquote><q>...turned away from the &quot;great Marxist or functionalist systems&quot; by reducing the scale of their observation of historical processes so as to &quot;obtain a more realistic description of human behavior.&quot; They saw social action as &quot;the result of an individual's constant negotiation, manipulation, choices and decisions in the face of a normative reality which, though pervasive, nevertheless offers many possibilities for personal interpretations and freedoms.&quot;(9)</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>不过照Sewell看来，年鉴学派到现在的著作，依然没表明他们的那个宏大目标——既能宏观也能着眼微观进程——实现到哪里。法国历史学家的新定义有多大效力尚未可知，但可以说他们还是逃不过美国和英国的风潮，必须重估自己的理论体系。

                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







